    <string name="tutorial_intro">QuizCards is an application that allows you to learn and study
        about different topics based on the ANKI learning algorithm. Inside of the application
        you will find different decks that will contain cards with questions
        inside to test your knowledge.</string>

    <string name="tutorial_question1">How can I add a new card to a deck?</string>
    <string name="tutorial_answer1">Within the desired deck you will find its corresponding
    list of cards, below this list you will find an option to add the type of
    card you want. It is very similar to adding a deck in the app</string>

    <string name="tutorial_question2">Is there any navigation aid?</string>
    <string name="tutorial_answer2">The user will have at all times a menu that can be
    unfold by dragging your finger across the screen from left to right which will offer you a
    view of the different sections of the application and you can access them through these
    shortcuts.</string>

    <string name="tutorial_footer">For any further questions, please contact
    the app developer</string>

